---
title: Stuffed Red Peppers with Moroccan-Spiced Pork and Herby Quinoa
description: This Moroccan spice blend is pretty top-notch. Loaded with warm, fragrant spices like cumin and ginger, it has a way of transforming anything it touches. Here, it's used to season pork, which is then stuffed into tender roasted bell peppers and served on a bed of quinoa.
